International Ferro May Conclude Loan Deal With Chinese Bank in 4-6 Weeks

-- B y   C a r l i   L o u r e n s
-- 
2011-04-20T07:06:18Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-20/international-ferro-may-conclude-loan-deal-with-chinese-bank-in-4-6-weeks.html
International Ferro Metals Ltd. (IFL) 
said a loan facility it’s negotiating through the South African
branch of a Chinese bank to fund a chrome-recovery plant may
take four to six weeks to conclude.  The ferrochrome producer also has “a few other” funding
plans, Chief Executive Officer David Kovarsky said in a phone
interview today, declining to be more specific.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Carli Lourens at 
 clourens@bloomberg.net  